attributes.review: I opened this app and my tree husband went missing. So I went to Wells Fargo on my donkey to talk to the mAnAgEr. But the line for smoothies was too long so I left on my lizard. When I got to the store I saw some turkey sandwiches so I ate them. I saw a cute baby. I left the tomato with my toes and went home to find a letter. My tree husband was in a vacation in 1942 and said he would meet me at 1976. Then I reopened the app and I went to 1977 and missed him. Overall I would give it a 7/10 <3 :)
